                  <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Reader:</strong> desktop, fixed, gate, OEM module or handheld device that communicates with the credential.</li>
                  <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Application:</strong> access control, attendance, inventory, logistics, laundry, NFC content delivery and more.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
